1195) to the\nproblem of Asmus Schmidt about generalized Ap\\'ery's numbers. Finally, Chapter\n7 is about expressing the special $L$-values as periods (in the sense of\nKontsevich and Zagier), in particular, as values of hypergeometric functions;\nit is based on the publication in Springer Proc. Math. Stat. 43 (2013),\n381--395.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Dec 2013 04:38:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-30"}
